{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"42e735746f","title":"向党委进一言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf7a956340","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":24,"articleId":"42e735746f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1c1b123f49","type":"title","text":"向党委进一言","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"091759f315","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"1a662ec86f","type":"paragraph","text":"人们早已睁大眼，竖起耳，听候学校整风的动静。可是这些日子，却有点失望了！我们学校的整风总起来是给人一个这样的印象：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"8cfd0bb6c9","type":"paragraph","text":"和风细雨   有风无雨","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"6523290b48","type":"paragraph","text":"变成","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"74cb824b81","type":"paragraph","text":"党内整风   关门整风","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"e60f8b4014","type":"paragraph","text":"何为有风无雨？刘副院长的动员报告，从头到尾只是动员群众提意见，未作半句自我批评，未揭露任何问题，群众顾虑还很多，打开第一期整风专刊一看，尽是“机关作风正在逐渐清除，但工作中还有一些痕迹”，“与党员相处，开诚布公说得上，推心置腹却不够”之类，可是为什么却把一些老教授整出了神经病呢？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"c6a523e315","type":"paragraph","text":"何谓关门整风？照党委的计划，学生、非党职工，只能按照组织提意见。至于学校到底存在什么问题，如何整，整的结果怎样？始终无法过问。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"ac88fbd77c","type":"paragraph","text":"因此我向党委进一言：除三害是要下决心的，关起门来羞答答地是不能解决问题的，我建议：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"db38316cfd","type":"paragraph","text":"1、割尾巴要脱裤子，主动地把“内幕”向群众揭开，公开地作自我批评，这样才能打破群众的顾虑。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"b6e58f249d","type":"paragraph","text":"2、破除一切提意见的清规戒律，让学校中从教授至工友通过大字报、壁报、集会、自由讲台各种形式说出自己要说的话。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"b2fe8eb620","type":"paragraph","text":" 笔者  学生证  567160号","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"da8ad5b1f4","type":"paragraph","text":"两点说明：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"0e0a09d1d0","type":"paragraph","text":"①为什么用大字报形式？A．一湖死水只有投上一块巨石，才能激起浪花，B．一切妨碍批评的清规戒律去他的，我带头破除。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"104e26139c","type":"paragraph","text":"②为什么以学号代姓名？A．免得为某些“正人君子”指风头主义哗众取宠，B．有学号可查，免被怀疑为“××分子捣乱”。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"},{"id":"08b8ed87b4","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《北京政法学院右派分子言行汇编》(第3部分)(北京政法学院，1957年10月)。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f"}],"page":{"id":"3bb8ccb678","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"42e735746f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}